    investorTakeaways: ["Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP, and Dogecoin have seen substantial price drops, triggering an 'extreme fear' sentiment across the market.", "Despite bearish sentiment, on-chain data shows historically low cryptocurrency supplies on exchanges, often a precursor to accumulation phases.", "Stablecoin issuer Circle has achieved a significant regulatory milestone by securing approval to operate as a bank, enhancing its legitimacy."],
