    featuredImagePrompt: "A striking visual representation of regulatory oversight on Big Tech. A large, stylized 'EU' emblem or a metaphorical government hand, rendered in European Union flag colors (blue and yellow), firmly but fairly holding or hovering over a distorted, abstract representation of the Meta logo (the blue infinity loop). The background subtly suggests digital networks and perhaps faint, blurred figures interacting with screens, hinting at user impact and online scams. The overall tone is serious and authoritative, using a clean, modern, industry-specific visual style. The composition should convey pressure and accountability, with a focus on the regulatory body's influence over the tech giant. Emphasize a sense of control and oversight without being overly aggressive.",
