    featuredImagePrompt: "A data-driven visual contrasting two financial charts side-by-side. On the left, a downward-trending line graph with red accents representing India's Nifty 50 index, showing a sharp drop to 25,800 with a large '₹2.8 Lakh Crore Selloff' annotation. On the right, an upward-trending bar chart or candlestick chart with green accents, depicting positive investor sentiment and successful IPO performances, featuring subtle logos or stylized representations of 'Klarna' and 'SpaceX'. The background is a sophisticated, clean interface with subtle global market data elements. The overall aesthetic is clean, professional, and informative, using a modern color palette of blues, greens, and reds for emphasis. The composition should clearly show a contrast between decline and growth.",
