    featuredImagePrompt: "An editorial news layout featuring a split screen. On one side, a stylized graphic of a stock market chart showing an upward trend with a globe overlay, symbolizing global recovery and easing geopolitical tensions. On the other side, a subtle, blurred background image of a corporate office building (Salesforce Tower) with a downward-pointing red arrow graphic overlaid, representing the downgrade. In the foreground, a magnifying glass focused on a small-cap stock ticker (IWM) on a digital screen, signifying trader interest. The overall aesthetic is professional, clean, and dynamic, suitable for a financial news platform.",
