      bullCase: "The bullish case for this trend rests on the continued exponential growth of AI and space technologies, sustained investor appetite for disruptive innovation, and the further legitimization of alternative assets. Successful IPOs from firms like OpenAI and SpaceX would unlock massive capital, fuel further R&D, and create new market leaders. Increased integration of crypto into traditional finance could lead to broader adoption, higher liquidity, and new financial products, driving overall market expansion.",
