      neutralCase: "This incident is a natural, albeit costly, part of the adversarial and competitive MEV landscape. It represents an evolution in bot capabilities and counter-capabilities, without fundamentally altering the underlying dynamics of MEV extraction or the overall growth trajectory of DeFi, which continues to innovate despite such setbacks.",
      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "The most probable outcome is a continued \'arms race\' in MEV, with both offensive and defensive strategies becoming more sophisticated. There\'s a high probability of increased focus on security and MEV mitigation from protocol developers, alongside persistent, albeit evolving, bot activity. Overall sentiment impact is likely medium-term neutral, with short-term caution.",
      potentialCatalysts: ["Discovery and public disclosure of the exploit vector.", "New MEV-resistant protocol launches gaining significant adoption.", "Increased regulatory clarity or enforcement regarding front-running."],
