      potentialCatalysts: ["Successful launch and adoption of new Ethereum upgrades (e.g., scalability solutions) by community-led initiatives.", "Clear articulation and execution of EthLabs\' research agenda, demonstrating its value.", "Strong market recovery for Bitcoin and other major cryptocurrencies, lifting overall sentiment.", "Increased institutional adoption of Ethereum-based solutions and DeFi applications.", "Development of robust, decentralized governance and funding mechanisms within the Ethereum ecosystem."],
