    quickAnswer: "The crypto market is seeing MemeCore\'s M token crash over 74% amid insider manipulation concerns, Bitcoin\'s $59,000 support level face a test from the U.S. Core PCE report, and Ripple\'s RLUSD stablecoin gain regulatory approval in Japan.",
