    investorTakeaways: ["Exercise extreme caution with meme tokens, especially those with unverified teams, concentrated supply, or thin liquidity, as they carry significant manipulation and volatility risks.", "Monitor global macroeconomic data, particularly U.S. inflation reports like Core PCE, as they can significantly impact Bitcoin\'s price and broader crypto market sentiment.", "Consider the long-term implications of regulatory clarity for stablecoins; Ripple\'s success in Japan could pave the way for more widespread institutional adoption in regulated markets.", "Prioritize due diligence and seek assets with transparent tokenomics, strong utility, and established regulatory compliance to mitigate risks.", "Diversify portfolios and understand that different crypto segments (meme coins, stablecoins, blue-chip assets) have vastly different risk-reward profiles."],
